snippet.title: Championship Manager: Season 00/01 gameplay (PC Game, 2000)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Championship Manager: Season 00/01, PC game produced by Eidos in 2000 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/championship-manager-season-00-01/12231/
Playing as Barcelona manager the first part of 2000/2001 season. Winning first qualifying match for Champions league and loosing a friendly against Milan.
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Championship Manager: Season 01/02 - https://youtu.be/0R8E06LrMHo
Championship Manager: Season 99/00  - https://youtu.be/hswlAhqnQNM
Premier Manager 97 - https://youtu.be/rJ3ftb_Pkww
